Provisions were up from Pounds 7.3m in 1990 to Pounds 33.7m last year,
driving the society's pre-tax profits down by 13 per cent from Pounds 73.6m
to Pounds 64m.
Total group assets rose by 15 per cent in 1991 to Pounds 8.5bn (Pounds
