FT  09 MAR 92 / Construction Contracts: Building defence facility
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
WIMPEY ENGINEERING AND CONSTRUCTION (EUROPE) has secured a Pounds 35m
contract from the Property Services Agency to construct the main joint
maritime communications centre at RAF St Mawgan in Cornwall.
The project includes the construction of three linked buildings and all
associated external works, drainage and landscaping. Completion is scheduled
for September 1994.
